<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-3198]  DefaultCamelContext throws NPE in getRoute(String id)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-3198</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt; DefaultCamelContext throws NPE in getRoute(String id) if no routes are deployed.&lt;br/&gt;
This happens because the &quot;route LinkedHashSet&quot; is not initialized.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fix:&lt;br/&gt;
 don&apos;t do Lazy init of route  or add this to getRoute(String id):&lt;br/&gt;
 if (routes == null) &lt;/p&gt;
{
	routes = new LinkedHashSet&amp;lt;Route&amp;gt;();
 }
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

</description>
